## ​Quick Install (Recommended)

​

```
curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSfL https://install.arcium.com/ | bash
```


```
curl --proto '=https' --tlsv1.2 -sSfL https://install.arcium.com/ | bash
```


```
arcup
```

[here](https://docs.arcium.com/developers/installation/arcup)
- Check for all required dependencies
- Install Linux build dependencies automatically (if needed)
- Download and install arcup for your platform
- Install the latest Arcium CLI (command-line interface for interacting with the Arcium network and managing computations)
- Install the Arx Node (the core node software that performs encrypted computations in the network)

```
arcup
```

### ​Prerequisites

​
- Rust: Install from [here](https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install)
- Solana CLI 2.3.0: Install from [here](https://docs.solana.com/cli/install-solana-cli-tools), then run solana-keygen new
- Yarn: Install from [here](https://yarnpkg.com/getting-started/install)
- Anchor 0.32.1: Install from [here](https://www.anchor-lang.com/docs/installation)
- Docker & Docker Compose: Install Docker from [here](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/) and Docker Compose from here
[here](https://www.rust-lang.org/tools/install)
[here](https://docs.solana.com/cli/install-solana-cli-tools)

```
solana-keygen new
```

[here](https://yarnpkg.com/getting-started/install)
[here](https://www.anchor-lang.com/docs/installation)
[here](https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/)
[here](https://docs.docker.com/compose/install/)

## ​Manual Installation
​
[here](https://docs.arcium.com/developers/installation/arcup)

```
arcup
```

- aarch64_linux
- x86_64_linux
- aarch64_macos
- x86_64_macos

```
aarch64_linux
```


```
x86_64_linux
```


```
aarch64_macos
```


```
x86_64_macos
```


```
<YOUR_TARGET>
```


```
TARGET=aarch64_linux && curl "https://bin.arcium.com/download/arcup_${TARGET}_0.4.0" -o ~/.cargo/bin/arcup && chmod +x ~/.cargo/bin/arcup
```


```
TARGET=aarch64_linux && curl "https://bin.arcium.com/download/arcup_${TARGET}_0.4.0" -o ~/.cargo/bin/arcup && chmod +x ~/.cargo/bin/arcup
```


```
arcup
```


```
arcup install
```


```
arcup install
```


```
arcium --version
```


```
arcium --version
```

## ​Issues
​

### ​Platform-Specific Issues
​

```
sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade && sudo apt-get install -y pkg-config build-essential libudev-dev libssl-dev
```


```
sudo apt-get update && sudo apt-get upgrade && sudo apt-get install -y pkg-config build-essential libudev-dev libssl-dev
```

### ​Incorrect $PATH
​

```
$PATH
```


```
arcup
```


```
arcium
```


```
~/.cargo/bin
```


```
PATH
```


```
PATH
```


```
which arcium
```


```
which arcium
```


```
/home/user/.cargo/bin/arcium
```


```
/home/user/.cargo/bin/arcium
```


```
which arcium
```

- 
Bash/Zsh: Add to ~/.bashrc or ~/.zshrc:
CopyAsk AIexport PATH="$HOME/.cargo/bin:$PATH"


- 
Fish: Add to ~/.config/fish/config.fish:
CopyAsk AIset -gx PATH $HOME/.cargo/bin $PATH



```
~/.bashrc
```


```
~/.zshrc
```


```
export PATH="$HOME/.cargo/bin:$PATH"
```


```
export PATH="$HOME/.cargo/bin:$PATH"
```


```
~/.config/fish/config.fish
```


```
set -gx PATH $HOME/.cargo/bin $PATH
```


```
set -gx PATH $HOME/.cargo/bin $PATH
```


```
source ~/.bashrc
```

